      "text": [
        ": سألت أبا عبد الله عن الأئمة، فقال: مَن أنكر واحداً من الأحياء فقد أنكر الأموات."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.abdullah-al-shahin": [
          "(5) Muhammad bin Ya’qoob narrated from al-Husayn bin Muhammad from al-Mu’alla from ibn Jumhoor from Safwan that ibn Miskan had said: I asked Abu Abdullah as-Sadiq (as) about the imams and he said: “Whoever denies one of the alive imams, has denied the dead ones.”"
        ]
